extendedInfo.description: Crazy Dentist Office Free Game Tiny Teeth Makeover Story Fun Free Virtual Kids GameHelp the Ranger and his Friends clean their teeth.  First get your dentist license by passing the dentist training course and then work on cleaning your patients teeth.  After you clean your patients teeth don't forget to change decorate the teeth with tons of colors and teeth decorations.This is the Free version, the full version of the dentist office game includes: Features:- 2 patients- 7 dentist tools (Water, Drill, File, Plyers, Pick, Toothbrush, Suction)- Tons of colors to decorate with- Tons of tooth decorations (Diamonds, Skulls, Dollar signs, Happy Faces, etc...)Don't forget to check out our other fun games at https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Free+Cooking+GamesCrazy Dentist Office Free Game Tiny Teeth Makeover Story Fun Free Virtual Kids Game
